Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.95,0:01:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{?}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.05,0:01:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dr. Warumon's robot!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.81,0:02:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.83,0:02:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.19,0:02:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still kicking. But that impact sure was huge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.19,0:02:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{???}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.58,0:02:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's packing a 40mm cannon, at least!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.45,0:02:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's disperse now and close in on it!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.09,0:02:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Split up its attacks!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.98,0:02:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.80,0:02:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.96,0:02:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They split into three?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.79,0:02:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, they're underestimating this mech! {/robot}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.15,0:02:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,ZakoBee, don't say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.13,0:02:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they call themselves TwinBee, \Nthey're still just a bunch of middle school brats.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.50,0:02:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This Devil Gunner is nothing \Nlike the old anti-TwinBee machines. {should twinbee be capitalized if it's probably a type here and not proper name?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.19,0:02:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're about to learn that it's deadly serious. \NWritten “ultimate,” read as “guaranteed kill.”
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.92,0:02:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost makes you feel sorry for them.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.77,0:02:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too kind, Master!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.42,0:02:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not kind at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.95,0:03:01.36,Top,,0,0,0,,Yes, truly! How well and truly kind you are, it's unbearable! {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.62,0:03:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm about to destroy\NCinnamon's precious TwinBee
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.72,0:03:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,because he's been a thorn in \N my side since we were schoolboys.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, my ZakoBee crew! {zakobee-domo - kinda like saying "my minions"} {"crew" could also be "swarm"}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.86,0:03:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Show them the power of our strongest machine, \Nthe Devil Gunner, which cost our entire fortune!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.74,0:03:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, fire!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.64,0:03:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! {instead of bee their shtick is "waru" = bad/evil (warumon means "bad thing/evil guy")}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.16,0:03:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Got— H-Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.89,0:03:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's going on? \NWhy aren't they firing?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, the bullets won't come out!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.71,0:03:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.75,0:03:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.86,0:03:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.46,0:03:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it, Mint?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be all of them dismantled.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.15,0:03:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But why didn't that mech even try to attack?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.66,0:03:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing Dr. Warumon, he probably\Nspent too long ranting about Dr. Cinnamon
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.42,0:03:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and how this mech is nothing like \Nanything he's built before.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sounds about right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.22,0:03:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Those brats will pay for patronizing me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.78,0:04:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show them this mech\N{\i1}is{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}truly nothing like before!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.46,0:04:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,ZakoBees! Activate the deadly attack mode! {lit: certain kill technique} {could do "My ZakoBee crew/swarm!" again}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.48,0:04:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy to oblige! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.19,0:04:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Deadly attack setup initiated!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.54,0:04:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.49,0:04:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.43,0:04:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should finish it off just in case?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go! {?????????}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The head's out!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.31,0:04:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And the arms!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And the legs!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.75,0:04:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.78,0:04:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The enormous belly! {?????????? heira? tail? penis? not a clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.32,0:04:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.89,0:04:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still transforming!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there, sir! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.90,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.19,0:04:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to be amazed, TwinBees!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.27,0:04:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,With this ultimate deadly attack, you're finished!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.86,0:04:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It flew!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what a lame-looking mech! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.04,0:05:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that it's transformed, \Nit looks pretty impressive!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go! Deadly Attack!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.33,0:05:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavenly Kick! {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.37,0:05:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoke blockade! {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.31,0:05:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't work!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.91,0:05:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! W-We can't dodge it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.24,0:05:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ribbon Attack!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.06,0:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! You think that could stop me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But it worked! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.42,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're defeated! {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Direct hit!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.54,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!\NOur entire fortune went into that machine!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for this, TwinBees!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.81,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay you back one day. One day!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, you're in no position to threaten them.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.30,0:06:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait! Next time \Nwe have money, you're finished!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.26,0:06:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that Dr. Warumon is such a pain!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.91,0:06:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's clean this up and head back to the lab.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.88,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right, Light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is it, Mint?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.40,0:06:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee! There's wreckage mixed in \Nthat's not from Warumon's mech!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee! WinBee, are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.66,0:06:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, where?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.46,0:06:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, this doesn't look\Nlike anything from Earth!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? TwinBee, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.96,0:06:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be a UFO? \NWhy though?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.26,0:06:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Pastel's ribbon sliced right through the mech, \Nso maybe you hit them at the same time?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.29,0:06:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I don't know anything about that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.79,0:06:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee! There's something like blood!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.93,0:06:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... that's kinda gross.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.27,0:06:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,From the looks of it, \NI don't think there are any survivors.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.34,0:06:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do we do, Light?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.75,0:07:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What if that UFO was a peaceful envoy, \Nand I just caused an intergalactic war?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.73,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee! Pastel! I'm getting some life signals nearby!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.95,0:07:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, where?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.66,0:07:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll save you now!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.27,0:07:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang tight!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.66,0:07:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this thing? {???? maybe what'd you do}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.66,0:07:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The life signal was caused by {\i1}this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.66,0:07:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't just stand there!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.41,0:07:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever think about helping?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Did that hurt?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Dr. Cinnamon, did you find anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.37,0:07:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... From the chromosome and DNA analysis, \Nit's definitely not an earthling.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what planet it's from?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.25,0:08:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That much, I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.52,0:08:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, strangely, the dead aliens from the ship \Nand this baby seem to be different species.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.60,0:08:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not the child of those dead aliens?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.94,0:08:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely not.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.91,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way to find\Nwhere this child came from?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee! Smart as ever, Mint!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He's got an idea?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.13,0:08:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If Angel contacts satellites around Earth \Nand traces the UFO's path backward, {Angel Computer - A supercomputer located in Cinnamon's laboratory.}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.13,0:08:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we might figure out where it came from.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, that's brilliant!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.83,0:08:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel, can you start right away?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.86,0:08:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Dr. Cinnamon.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.17,0:08:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It may take some time.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.93,0:08:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Angel.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.83,0:08:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{? sounds of searching?}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.22,0:08:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we'll make sure to\Nget you back home, okay? {boku? poku?}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.02,0:08:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, w-what are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.73,0:08:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't grope me {\i1}there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.72,0:08:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{bee}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.82,0:09:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! He's trying to suck on Pastel's breast! {??????????? maybe "clings to pastel" or something? pastel no **** teru bii - maybe nomo/nomu something? to drink?}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.27,0:09:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.90,0:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? \NHey, cut it out! Hey! I said stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.81,0:09:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just watch, do something!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it wants milk? {lit: drink the boobs}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That could be it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya got any breast milk, Pastel?! {lit: does it come out}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! He's crying now!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.52,0:09:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Let's give him Mint's baby bottle!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Mint, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.69,0:09:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Mint? Why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.57,0:09:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go get some milk already, TwinBee! {lit: make }
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez! What do we do now?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.90,0:09:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee! It sure looks like he enjoys it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.43,0:09:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.32,0:09:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.82,0:09:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Mint, don't get mad. \NAfter all, that alien is even younger than you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if it isn't Madoka?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.65,0:10:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Light? Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.57,0:10:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No one was in the Log House, \Nso I just came here. {I assume log house next to this place is where they usually live/hang out? she says "I came in without permission"}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Pastel, whose baby is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.77,0:10:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this one? Well, this little guy...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.33,0:10:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.19,0:10:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Pastel, when did you... {became a mom/have the time to}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.81,0:10:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cruel!\NYou didn't even tell me!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just awful!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute! Madoka!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.65,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Light! Why are you just spacing out?! \NGo and stop her already!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.24,0:10:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Aye...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.29,0:10:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.45,0:10:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finished the task \Nof tracing the UFO's trajectory.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.94,0:10:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.58,0:10:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. So where did it come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In the direction of Venus.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Venus?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.73,0:11:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, I can't believe we've\Ngotta go all the way to Venus now.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.17,0:11:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just abandon this baby, can we?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.04,0:11:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess...\NDo people even live there?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.33,0:11:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.20,0:11:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Venus is covered in carbon dioxide, \Nso it's not an environment humans can live in.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.25,0:11:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, we can already see it. \NLet's land and check it out.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.23,0:11:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, descending to Venus!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.85,0:11:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a city on Venus?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.24,0:11:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we get inside?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.18,0:11:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we can enter from over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.12,0:12:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.58,0:12:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.39,0:12:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside this dome,\Nthe atmosphere is just like Earth!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.44,0:12:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's drop the\Nbaby off and head home.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.11,0:12:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Light! You're seriously just\Ngonna leave the baby here? {okizari = orphan / abandon}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.68,0:12:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.05,0:12:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.25,0:12:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't like simply returning\Na stray raccoon to the mountains!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.39,0:12:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't go home until we take\Nthe baby to its actual parents!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.32,0:12:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Such a pain...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.87,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This guy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mint, got any ideas?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.58,0:12:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.81,0:12:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.91,0:12:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.05,0:12:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Mint?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mint says he'll help.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.97,0:12:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The police!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.03,0:12:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This place must surely have \Nsome kind of police of their own.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.48,0:12:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of our genius little brother!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's find the police first.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.14,0:12:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But what are Venus police even like?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.21,0:12:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that must be them. Officer!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... I've got a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.60,0:13:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, flying cars there! \NFly down to the ground and step out! {lit: driver over there, descend to the ground}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.73,0:13:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe this baby is from Venus. \NCould you help us find his parents?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{all their belts and caps say VEN[US]}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.05,0:13:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do know him?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.40,0:13:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like that reaction...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.74,0:13:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize them!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold up! Get off me! {?????? ***** yamero}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, Light!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{papu}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? What...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I? {/what is this place}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.44,0:13:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What...?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.67,0:13:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.62,0:13:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What... What is this?! \NHey, take it off me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.97,0:13:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is this that thing UFOs do... \Ncattle mutilation?! Stop it! {nc what's that kyattomyu but it has to be a shortening of "cattle mutilation"}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.57,0:13:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I only... When we took down \NDr. Warumon's mech,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.11,0:13:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a UFO crashed alongside it, \Ninside which we found a baby
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.64,0:13:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that we thought came from Venus, \Nso we brought him here!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.22,0:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's going on? \NHurry up and take this thing off me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.33,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, even if it was out of ignorance, \Nwe owe you an apology.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. Now that we've cleared \N things up, it's all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.57,0:14:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! That would be beneath me as a king. {???? *** ni kakawaru}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.00,0:14:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you've saved Prince Soldonar, \Nthe rightful heir to the throne of Venus! {??? his name is not mentioned in any external source so I don't know exactly how to romanize it, or what it even sounds like... sorudonaru?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.12,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{???}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That baby is the prince?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.15,0:14:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.41,0:14:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.42,0:14:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.67,0:14:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mint is asking how the prince \Nof Venus ended up on Earth.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.01,0:14:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll be happy to explain. \NCome closer, won't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.56,0:14:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, how did the prince end up on Earth?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.08,0:15:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,An organization known as the\N“Devils of the Galaxy” kidnapped him for ransom.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.90,0:15:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, while the radar operator looked away \Nfor a moment, they entered the dome of Venus, {??? reidaa *** ga}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.45,0:15:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and when the soldiers looked away for a moment, \Nthey infiltrated the palace,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.43,0:15:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and while the prince's attendant looked away \Nfor a moment, they got close to him,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.86,0:15:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and then while everyone looked away \Nfor {\i1}just{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}a moment, they took advantage of that, and... {lit: in that opening}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.14,0:15:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we get it already.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.83,0:15:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So the dead aliens in the crashed UFO \Nmust've been the kidnappers. {/corpses}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.18,0:15:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a relief... {???}{She's clearly saying Chotto here, I think. Idk what you could put here though. -Marty}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.08,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They were probably planning \Nto hide the prince on Earth.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, the prince has\Nbeen safely returned.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.96,0:15:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Brave heroes, we welcome\Nyou as honored guests! {state guest}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, everyone! Let us feast!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Venus!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.19,0:15:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this actually looks like \Na pretty comfy place. Right, Pastel? {??????? oi nanka ******* deru kara - oishi? hoshi?}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.19,0:16:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to look! {this way/at me}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.91,0:16:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.96,0:16:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you finished changing? \NThis way, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... don't you have any other clothes for us?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, I'd like something else too...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.07,0:16:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they not please you? Those garments are \N the traditional ceremonial wear of our nation.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.35,0:16:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.14,0:16:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,These are...?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.12,0:16:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hm?}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.62,0:16:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah!}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you wearing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.77,0:16:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, you're one to talk!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.27,0:16:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like Kintaro or something! {probably because kintaro is traditionally drawn like this and because kin = 金 = gold (symbol on their aprons); their lines are a little different but I think they're both saying "kintaro"}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.72,0:16:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So embarrassing...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.78,0:16:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, please. A great crowd \Nof our loyal subjects has gathered to see you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.41,0:16:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A great crowd?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.60,0:16:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.00,0:17:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.00,0:17:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,People of Venus! The heroes \Nwho saved our prince have arrived!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, step forward, brave heroes!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.18,0:17:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Go on!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.14,0:17:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You go, Pastel.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.20,0:17:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Not dressed like {\i1}this{\i0} \Nin front of everyone! {/huge crowd}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.96,0:17:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What, with your butt in full view?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.62,0:17:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So is yours!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.75,0:17:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Now then, hero, a few words, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.71,0:17:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no... we weren't really trying to be heroes. {lit: not that kind of intention - not sure what he's about}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.96,0:17:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the TwinBee Team, \Nprefer to help people discreetly.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.90,0:17:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Showing off in public isn't really our thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.67,0:17:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Light...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.91,0:17:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid! You truly are heroes!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.86,0:17:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then at least show them your face.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.03,0:17:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.96,0:17:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hero! {yuusha-dono?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{same}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.71,0:17:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! This is your hero speaking!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.14,0:17:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.43,0:17:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.34,0:17:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever there's trouble in space, \Nleave it to the TwinBee Team!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.77,0:18:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Venus!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Venus!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, this looks good!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.58,0:18:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? \NCome to think of it, where's WinBee?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Light?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.44,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The TwinBees are getting \N fixed up somewhere else.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.37,0:18:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, they got pretty banged up \Nwhen we were arrested.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.38,0:18:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, eat up, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.87,0:18:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to hold back.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.73,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of dish is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.60,0:18:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the height of Venusian cuisine: salt-boiled\NVenus crab soup, found only in a certain region. {???? oosama, *** chiiki - maybe proper name? Obuda Area?}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.25,0:18:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And the crabs are so full of life \Nthat they shrug off boiling like it's nothing!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.49,0:18:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No one comes to Venus without trying it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.97,0:19:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The second course is grilled crab, \Nseared in flames ten thousand degrees hot.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.59,0:19:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! This one's pretty strong. {???????? kore ga **** no chikara}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.42,0:19:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The eyeball is the best part, \Nthe rest you toss aside.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyeball, you say?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.22,0:19:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Venus is too much for me... {???????? kinsei kamawan?}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.08,0:19:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's... quite a refined taste.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.44,0:19:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The hero praised my cooking as refined!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.75,0:19:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is! It's Venus crab! \NBring more Venus crab and keep 'em coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.11,0:19:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Right, you're still a baby, Prince. \NWhat's the matter? {??????? idk why she asks that? akachan janakute?}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.32,0:19:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he's completely taken with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.33,0:19:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, really? That's delightful. {/makes me kind of happy} \NBabies really are adorable.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.69,0:19:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.27,0:19:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you pouting about, Mint? \NHeh, getting jealous, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.49,0:19:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, stop! \NYou can't do that, Prince!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.72,0:19:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Light! This is bad! {taihen}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.74,0:19:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{Whoa!}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.34,0:20:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,WinBee, do something!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.20,0:20:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel's totally exposed! \NWe can see it all! We can totally see everything! {????????????? pastel ga *** bi! mieteru bi! **** ga mieteru bi!}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.36,0:20:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No you can't!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.43,0:20:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what was it that's “bad”? {taihen}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.62,0:20:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, it's bad! \NWe don't have any fuel to get back to Earth!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.78,0:20:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? So it leaked out\Nwhen you guys got damaged?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.65,0:20:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's just borrow some from this planet.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.03,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the problem! \NThey haven't that kind of fuel!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.20,0:20:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This planet doesn't mine or\Nproduce the kind of fuel we use!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.48,0:20:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.11,0:20:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what their chief science officer told me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.60,0:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.68,0:20:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.76,0:20:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, is it true there's no fuel on your planet like the kind we use?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.89,0:20:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If my chief scientist says so, \Nthen it must be true.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.21,0:20:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, we can't go back to Earth!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me. {lit: even if you say that to me}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.82,0:20:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.86,0:20:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mint, you got an idea?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.12,0:20:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.76,0:21:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, our bodies have \Na fuel-generating function,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.22,0:21:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so we don't have to always rely \Non mineral resources from outside. {sometimes i have to question if you can consider these robots intelligent at all}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.87,0:21:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then let's ask that chief scientist \Nabout alternative materials.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.17,0:21:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.72,0:21:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Or this?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.74,0:21:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.30,0:21:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.32,0:21:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.96,0:21:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.10,0:21:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, we still couldn't find any fuel.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.66,0:21:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This stinks. \NPastel was really worried about going back. {idk what's this weird -ka, maybe "and yet..."}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.99,0:21:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet she's sound asleep now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.20,0:21:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Pastel for you, thick-skinned as ever.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.72,0:21:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But what are we gonna do, Light? \NWhat happens to us now?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.80,0:21:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,With this heavy dome and dense atmosphere, \Nwe can't even send a signal.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.76,0:21:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can't ask Dr. Cinnamon for help either.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.97,0:21:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the next planet over, \Nbut it feels a whole lot farther now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.44,0:22:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.90,0:22:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still some snacks over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.76,0:22:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, sorry, but that\Nstuff's not exactly my cup of tea.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.20,0:22:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.09,0:22:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just suck it up and eat it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.83,0:22:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy for you to say.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.57,0:22:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.79,0:22:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Better than starving to death.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.78,0:22:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.94,0:22:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... Is this really all they've got?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.74,0:22:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To think we came all this way to help someone, \Nand now we're the ones in trouble!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.92,0:22:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Light! Getting mad just\Nmakes you even hungrier.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.54,0:22:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you don't always have to eat its eyeball. \NMaybe the legs taste better!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.96,0:22:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called Venus crab, after all! {idk what he means or if this is supposed to be a joke}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.96,0:22:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you try it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.70,0:22:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.86,0:22:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.64,0:22:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, on three... {Okay, one, two...}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:54.79,0:22:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong, TwinBee?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.61,0:22:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The fuel gauge just went up a little!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.78,0:23:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, TwinBee, does that mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.06,0:23:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee... I did {\i1}not{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}expect that. {?? maybe "I don't want to think about it"}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.25,0:23:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really leaving?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.94,0:23:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you for having us.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.03,0:23:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.90,0:23:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, I'm sorry,\Nbut it's time to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.81,0:23:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, you must let them go. {ikemasen}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.67,0:23:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.93,0:23:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.06,0:23:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel, Mint says give this to the prince!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.48,0:23:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.74,0:23:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.54,0:23:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Aria?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.45,0:23:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.38,0:23:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.11,0:23:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.57,0:23:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a 1:1 Pastel doll. The prince really liked Pastel, \Nso Mint made it just in case.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.57,0:23:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, thanks, Mint.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.91,0:23:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't know you had it in you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.66,0:23:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.75,0:24:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of this as me and take good care of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.43,0:24:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't use it for anything weird, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.84,0:24:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird, like...?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.92,0:24:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.61,0:24:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.74,0:24:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you to say it! {????? ***hazureta?}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.60,0:24:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, then! WinBee! {ja? bye?}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.65,0:24:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait up!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.19,0:24:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Launching!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.82,0:24:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again! {??? probably a mix of "mata kuru ne" and kinsei = venus}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:31.60,0:24:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Right... could that kid \Nactually be from Venus after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:36.00,0:24:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:37.84,0:24:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{maybe "hungry"}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:39.04,0:24:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,TwinBee, we're running low on fuel again!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:42.20,0:24:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What, already?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:44.15,0:24:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't complain, just eat it!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:45.60,0:24:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to! \NEasy for you to say "just eat it." {throwback to 22:09}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:48.76,0:24:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,WinBee, don't get mad. See, if you don't eat, \Nwe won't make it back to Earth.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:53.22,0:24:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but just eat, okay, everyone?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:56.65,0:24:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready... go! {Okay, on three...}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.02,0:24:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:59.27,0:25:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:01.59,0:25:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little more! \NHang in there, TwinBee!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:03.80,0:25:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, WinBee!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:05.42,0:25:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.50,0:25:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{?}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:12.08,0:25:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's topic: "Things I absolutely cannot eat!"
Dialogue: 10,0:25:17.77,0:25:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Starring:
Dialogue: 10,0:25:18.79,0:25:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,TwinBee—Mayumi "Rotten natto, no way am I eating that." Tanaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:22.78,0:25:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Pastel—Hekiru "Cockroaches." Shiina!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:27.05,0:25:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,WinBee—Kumiko "Monjayaki\Non a hangover day." Nishihara. {dish of pan-fried batter with various fillings}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:32.22,0:25:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mint and GwinBee—Miki "Buttercream." Ito.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:37.10,0:25:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Cinnamon—Kazumi "Celery." Tanaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:40.88,0:25:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Madoka—Mariko "Deep-fried kangaroo tail—no matter\Nhow good you say it is, I'm not eating it." Kokuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:52.46,0:25:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,ZakoBee—Yusuke "Ferns and wild vegetables." Numata.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:56.28,0:26:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince—Sumie "Sea urchin, salmon roe." Baba.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:00.53,0:26:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Venusian police—Koichi "Nothing." Sakaguchi . {meaning there's no thing he would never eat probs?}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:04.25,0:26:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,King—Daiki "Cold hamburgers, herring roe​." Nakamura.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:10.00,0:26:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen—Ryoka "Dog treats, leaf jerky." Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:15.10,0:26:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Warumon—Yukimasa
Dialogue: 10,0:26:17.33,0:26:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shiitake, milk, and miso soup, no matter\Nhow you cook them, I absolutely refuse." Kishino! {?????????? no clue at all what chiinaka yuuyuumisanu could be}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:23.84,0:26:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But you set us up! You did it! \NWe got into this mess because of you! Hey! {???????????????}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:28.98,0:26:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Light—Kappei "Crab miso." Yamaguchi.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:33.43,0:26:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:34.12,0:26:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But crab miso can be really good! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:36.01,0:26:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I just don't like it!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:37.31,0:26:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's all for today!
Comment: 0,0:26:39.67,0:26:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,
